id: pm-l709
title: "History & storage observability: pm gc locks scope, pm history --diff before/after, pm stats --storage"
description: "Combined PR delivering three history/storage observability primitives under epics pm-o2kc (storage/history/durability) and pm-mpbb (CLI surface): (1) pm gc locks scope — clean stale lock debris from crashed processes [pm-d70h, pm-gbbn]; (2) pm history --diff before/after field values + --field filter, enhancing the existing names-only --diff [pm-puvn, pm-g94b]; (3) pm stats --storage aggregate history-stream metrics (streams/lines/bytes/top-N by size+depth/oldest+newest) [pm-mnee]. Each feature's pure logic lives in an isolated src/core/** module (100% covered); orchestrator owns shared wiring (cli-contracts, MCP server, completion, docs)."
type: Plan
status: closed
priority: 2
