close_reason: "Plan complete: all 3 history/storage observability features shipped (gc locks scope, history --diff before/after + --field, stats --storage) via 3 isolated 100%-covered core modules + orchestrator wiring. Full gate green (142 files / 2423 tests, 100% coverage); manual e2e verified all paths."
plan_mode: draft
plan_scope: pm gc locks scope + pm history --diff values + pm stats --storage
plan_steps[1]{id,order,title,status,created_at,updated_at,evidence,completed_at}:
  plan-step-001,1,"Build isolated core modules (lock-gc, history-diff, history-storage-stats) via specialized sub-agents",completed,"2026-06-05T20:36:47.048Z","2026-06-05T21:19:13.151Z","Shipped via 3 isolated, 100%-covered core modules built by specialized sub-agents: core/lock/lock-gc.ts (runLockGc, 27 tests), core/history/history-diff.ts (computeHistoryDiff replaying via replay.ts primitives, 40 tests), core/history/history-storage-stats.ts (computeHistoryStorageStats pure aggregate, 31 tests). Orchestrator wired the command layer (gc/history/stats), contracts, MCP, completion, docs. DECISION: history --field exposed CLI-only (FLAG_CONTRACTS + completion + help) and NOT added to the MCP action schema, because the param key 'field' is already taken by create/update's repeatable --field name=value (array) — MCP pm_history returns the full changes[] for client-side filtering. DISCOVERY: --diff already existed but only emitted changed_field NAMES; enhanced to add changes:[{field,before,after}] values and made it independent of the compact/full projection. pm stats already aggregated streams; --storage adds top-N largest/deepest + oldest/newest. Full gate green: 142 files / 2423 tests, 100% coverage; manual e2e in temp tracker verified gc locks sweep (stale removed, active+unparseable retained), --diff/--field values, and stats --storage.","2026-06-05T21:19:13.151Z"
